Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:09.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I went camping with Haibara and the other three Detective Boys in Dr. Agasa's Beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:16.41,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The doc and I went off to buy some mess kits since they had been forgotten, and happened upon Masumi Sera.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:19.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She ended up deciding to camp with us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:25.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Meanwhile, Haibara and the Detective Boys went into the woods to gather firewood,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:30.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and ended up finding someone burying a woman's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A... woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being buried?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Unable to contact me, Haibara and the others ran for their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:44.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and ended up hiding in a cabin in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are things, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like there's only the one entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:00:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The floor was just wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me that woman was killed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, then the killer will almost certainly return to this blood-soaked crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then we have to hurry and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:29.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Around the same time, we met Inspector Yamamura, who had received a report from Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three possible suspects in burying the corpse{help?} were also found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been chained shut — we can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been locked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, can't you smell something burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain cabin's on fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:01:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This door won't budge one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do?! It's too strong for us to break...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody's sure to notice the smoke and come help us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:16.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right, Kudō{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's pretty far, but there's smoke rising up over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably just smoke from a campfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, there's one over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently, a lot of young people have been building huge wooden structures and throwing parties during the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here are the three men mentioned in the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I see. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:17.87,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeking comprehensive answers, he solves every mystery and code!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A black shadow approaching Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.42,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10} A small mistake left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:23.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, one by one, please tell me your name, occupation, and the reason why you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:27.30,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hayamichi Yonezumi (31)\NPart-Time Worker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:23.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm Hayamichi Yonezumi, a part-time worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:30.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on, but I came to check out the area, since I'm gonna be camping here with my buddies next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:38.22,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Chōzō Usagi (42)\NPhotographer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My name's Chōzō Usagi, I'm a photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:39.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm going around taking photos of the scenery of campsites all around Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:47.02,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Takeya Iwakuma (23)\NUniversity Student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.61,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I came to take photos too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:45.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Photos of Japanese azalea with my mobile phone camera, to post on my blog...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Orange flowers bloom on them at this time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My name's Takeya Iwakuma. I'm a fourth-year student at Beika University.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You three are pretty lightly equipped, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just scouting the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just taking a look around too — my camera and equipment are in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I just came for a quick visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still not connecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knowing Haibara, she should've moved to some place with reception, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she's still being chased around by the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then those three must be innocent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps, though it's not a nice idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone, possibly one of those three, already killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or they're in some situation that means they can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep your heads low, so you don't breathe in the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody will save us soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when are they gonna get here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-There's smoke coming up from over there too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it a campfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean they won't notice the smoke coming from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:13.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then all that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of you are 26 cm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our shoe sizes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:32.65,Thoughts,,10,10,0,,{\be10}Damn it! If the killer is one of those three, then the fastest way to find them would be to figure out who and ask him directly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the Detective Badges are back with the tents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go and search too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you search about blindly, you'll just get lost in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be best to leave the searching to the search party, who know the mountain well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's almost sunset, and even the shadows are growing longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't find them before it becomes dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:07.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi! Wake up, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, bring Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} closer to the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to give her some fresh air!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. Hang in there, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll move you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be breathing fresh mountain air in just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, breathe in, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ain't it great? Hey, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hang on, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi! Wake up, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounded like a door...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible — we're the only ones here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me the killer came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to tell us what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't explain what's going on, we can't exactly help you any further...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got plans, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:10:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Actually, a woman's corpse was abandoned on the mountain, and the killer's on the run...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we rounded up the three of you, who were wandering alone on the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you three show me both of your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been watching you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Yonezumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Iwakuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} have been only using their left hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Usagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has only been using his right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I thought you might be hiding some sort of injury on your other hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I use my left hand because I'm left-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing on my right hand, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm left-handed too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was using my right hand because I'm right-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, there is nothing on my left hand either...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Usagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was right-handed too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:11:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't see anything but the female corpse that the killer was trying to bury and the hole, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence that the killer was right-handed was left behind on the corpse and beside the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wound on the corpse was made by an axe-like object striking from the upper right downwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the guy who hacked at her was right-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the killer's footprints next to the hole show the left footprint in front, and the right one in the rear...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the person digging the hole wasn't right-handed, he wouldn't have left prints like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you mean he's the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you have any defence, I'd like to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't most people right-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These two could actually be right-handed too, just forcing themselves to use their left hand in order to hide it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:12:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the killer could even still be hiding somewhere in these mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, most Japanese people are right-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think there's only one person wandering around this mountain today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's both right handed and named 'Usagi' — and that's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Look here, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is that name in the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dead lady told us, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She made this shape with her fingers inside the sleeping bag she was shoved into, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how does that produce the name 'Usagi'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to tell just from the shapes of the fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but if you stack your right and left hands like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And shine light on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}usagi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-A rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But why a shadow puppet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she could have made this shape, she could have written something in blood too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because the murdered woman was a nursery teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nursery teachers often show children shadow puppets,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and even if the killer saw her hands, he wouldn't take it to be a rabbit at first glance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her hands probably came apart while she was being moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no use playing innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you left that big a wound on the victim's back, you must've ended up with a lot of blood splatter on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like you changed and tried to wash it off, but it's not so easy to remove...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood's reaction to luminol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't we just take those three to the station from the start and test for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we'd done that, it would've taken too long and delayed our search for the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My friends spotted you burying the corpse, and you chased them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}still{\i0} denying it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my fault, it was hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shutting me in a place like that as a prank...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the one who wronged me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I loved her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I proposed to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She went and did something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, what's this about shutting you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm claustrophobic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, I was shut inside a lift for a whole day due to an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since then, whenever I'm closed up in a dark place, I panic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But knowing that, she still attempted to shut me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a pitch-black cabin where even the windows wouldn't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it was the victim who brought you up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... Naturally, I panicked, and started swinging around the cabin axe to try and escape somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it ended up going into her back by accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she hadn't pulled that prank,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then those children wouldn't have been shut in there either...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut in inside that mountain cabin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably too late to save them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:36.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me he shut them in the cabin and set it on fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The search party reports that they've discovered a burning cabin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did they manage to put it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time they discovered the cabin, it was burning so fiercely that there was nothing they could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me go! My friends are inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta! Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara! Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're over here, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some lady we'd never seen before suddenly appeared and rescued us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She chopped the door down with the axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she'd been living in the attic of the mountain cabin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:17:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman said she rescued her first, and let her run away to a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we just got a phone call from Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, so we know she's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me she took the antidote...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did that woman go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told us to hide until you guys came, and went off over that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would like for the children come with us for police questioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They might have inhaled the smoke. They should see a doctor first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then if they could come to the station afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what kind of person that woman was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She kinda looked like Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I secretly took a video of her and sent it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sent a video...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We want to thank her properly later, so we sent it to the Mouri Detective Agency to find out who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd promised to send him photos from the camping trip, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, here she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think we'll see her next week even if we don't look for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believed a certain {\i1}someone{\i0} would save us and waited, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd have to take the antidote and turn back to my old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you get those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I borrowed some of the dead woman's clothes from the cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't about to show up naked in front of the kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I wasn't able to pull off this ring as my body had grown,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I changed all of my clothes, so I'm sure the kids couldn't tell I was Ai Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:19:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you better hide in a tent or somewhere until the drug wears off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll all be going for police questioning anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, you caught the killer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was a photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We figured it out from her dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said she locked him in that cabin even though he was claustrophobic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... That fits perfectly then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rucksack with her clothes in had a book about claustrophobia in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably planned to help him get over his phobia by having him spend a night in that cabin with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that ended up backfiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It made him panic, and he ended up killing her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about an unwelcome favour...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could've lived fine even without overcoming his fear like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was because he was a photographer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he kept using film cameras...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not being able to enter naturally dark and cramped darkrooms would have been a lethal blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to hurry him to being his former self again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But didn't she leave evidence saying that he was the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That shows that she held a grudge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it now, it wasn't really a dying message...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She just wanted to hold close to her in her final moments...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shape of her beloved Usagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So those brats are spending tonight at an inn in Gunma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Apparently they're still scared of staying at the campsite...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those brats sure get caught up in a lot of cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? I just heard some noise downstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just the wind... it's been pretty strong today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:24.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A password...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:28.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How do you two usually come up with passwords?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:30.83,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I use my birth date.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:34.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'd use 5563 since it can be read 'Ko-go-rō{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}'.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:37.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}N-No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:39.77,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What if it's a really long password that you can't memorise?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:42.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}5-5-6-3...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:47.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A video was delivered instead of photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So until your friends come, hide and don't make a sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:10.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A Mystery Train Pass Ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:13.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Bell Tree Express, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:18.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's being hacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:21.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is it?!
